1:1 paulov, apostolov ihsou cristou dia yelhmatov yeou,
 kai timoyeov o adelfov, th ekklhsia tou yeou th oush en
 korinyw sun toiv agioiv pasin toiv ousin en olh th acaia:
1:2 cariv umin kai eirhnh apo yeou patrov hmwn kai kuriou
 ihsou cristou.

1:3 euloghtov o yeov kai pathr tou kuriou hmwn ihsou cristou,
 o pathr twn oiktirmwn kai yeov pashv paraklhsewv,
1:4 o parakalwn hmav en pash th yliqei hmwn, eiv to dunasyai
 hmav parakalein touv en pash yliqei dia thv paraklhsewv
 hv parakaloumeya autoi upo tou yeou:
1:5 oti kaywv perisseuei ta payhmata tou cristou eiv hmav,
 outwv dia cristou perisseuei kai h paraklhsiv hmwn.
1:6 eite de ylibomeya, uper thv umwn paraklhsewv kai swthriav
 thv energoumenhv en upomonh twn autwn payhmatwn wn kai
 hmeiv pascomen, kai h elpiv hmwn bebaia uper umwn: eite
 parakaloumeya, uper thv umwn paraklhsewv kai swthriav,
1:7 eidotev oti wsper koinwnoi este twn payhmatwn, outwv
 kai thv paraklhsewv.
1:8 ou gar yelomen umav agnoein, adelfoi, uper thv yliqewv
 hmwn thv genomenhv hmin en th asia, oti kay uperbolhn ebarhyhmen
 uper dunamin, wste exaporhyhnai hmav kai tou zhn:
1:9 alla autoi en eautoiv to apokrima tou yanatou eschkamen,
 ina mh pepoiyotev wmen ef eautoiv, all epi tw yew tw egeironti
 touv nekrouv:
1:10 ov ek thlikoutou yanatou errusato hmav kai ruetai,
 eiv on hlpikamen oti kai eti rusetai,
1:11 sunupourgountwn kai umwn uper hmwn th dehsei, ina ek
 pollwn proswpwn to eiv hmav carisma dia pollwn eucaristhyh
 uper hmwn.

1:12 h gar kauchsiv hmwn auth estin, to marturion thv suneidhsewv
 hmwn, oti en aplothti kai eilikrineia yeou, ouk en sofia
 sarkikh, all en cariti yeou anestrafhmen en tw kosmw, perissoterwv
 de prov umav.
1:13 ou gar alla grafomen umin, all h a anaginwskete h kai
 epiginwskete, elpizw de oti kai ewv telouv epignwsesye,
1:14 kaywv kai epegnwte hmav apo merouv, oti kauchma umwn
 esmen, kayaper kai umeiv hmwn, en th hmera tou kuriou ihsou.
1:15 kai tauth th pepoiyhsei eboulomhn prov umav elyein
 proteron, ina deuteran carin echte,
1:16 kai di umwn dielyein eiv makedonian, kai palin apo
 makedoniav elyein prov umav kai uf umwn propemfyhnai eiv
 thn ioudaian.
1:17 touto oun boulomenov mhti ara th elafria ecrhsamhn;
 h a bouleuomai, kata sarka bouleuomai, ina h par emoi to
 nai nai kai to ou ou;
1:18 pistov de o yeov oti o logov hmwn o prov umav ouk egeneto
 nai kai ou.
1:19 o gar tou yeou uiov ihsouv cristov o en umin di hmwn
 khrucyeiv, di emou kai silouanou kai timoyeou, ouk egeneto
 nai kai ou, alla nai en autw gegonen:
1:20 osai gar epaggeliai yeou, en autw to nai kai en autw
 to amhn, tw yew prov doxan di hmwn.
1:21 o de bebaiwn hmav sun umin eiv criston kai crisav hmav
 yeov,
1:22 o kai sfragisamenov hmav kai douv ton arrabwna tou
 pneumatov en taiv kardiaiv hmwn.

1:23 egw de martura ton yeon epikaloumai epi thn emhn quchn,
 oti feidomenov umwn ouketi hlyon eiv korinyon.
1:24 ouc oti kurieuomen umwn thv pistewv, alla sunergoi
 esmen thv carav umwn: th gar pistei esthkate.

2:1 ekrina de emautw touto, to mh palin en luph elyein prov
 umav.
2:2 ei gar egw lupw umav, kai tiv estin o eufrainwn me ei
 mh o lupoumenov ex emou;
2:3 kai egraqa umin touto auto, ina mh elywn luphn ecw af
 wn edei me cairein, pepoiywv epi pantav umav oti h emh
 cara pantwn umwn estin.
2:4 ek gar pollhv yliqewv kai sunochv kardiav egraqa umin
 dia pollwn dakruwn, ouc ina luphyhte, alla thn agaphn ina
 gnwte hn ecw perissoterwv eiv umav.

2:5 ei de tiv leluphken, ouk eme leluphken, alla, apo merouv
 ina mh epibarw, pantav umav.
2:6 ikanon tw toioutw h epitimia auth h upo twn pleionwn:
2:7 wste tounantion mallon umav carisasyai kai parakalesai,
 mhpwv th perissotera luph katapoyh o toioutov.
2:8 dio parakalw umav kurwsai eiv auton agaphn.
2:9 eiv touto gar kai egraqa, ina gnw thn dokimhn umwn,
 ei eiv panta uphkooi este.
2:10 w de ti carizesye, kai egw: kai gar egw ei ti kecarismai
 w kecarismai, di umav en proswpw cristou,
2:11 ina mh pleonekthywmen upo tou satana: ou gar autou
 ta nohmata agnooumen.

2:12 elywn de eiv thn trwada eiv to euaggelion tou cristou,
 kai yurav moi anewgmenhv en kuriw,
2:13 ouk eschka anesin tw pneumati mou tw mh eurein me titon
 ton adelfon mou, alla apotaxamenov autoiv exhlyon eiv makedonian.

2:14 tw de yew cariv tw pantote yriambeuonti hmav en tw
 cristw kai thn osmhn thv gnwsewv autou fanerounti di hmwn
 en panti topw:
2:15 oti cristou euwdia esmen tw yew en toiv swzomenoiv
 kai en toiv apollumenoiv,
2:16 oiv men osmh yanatou eiv yanaton, oiv de osmh zwhv
 eiv zwhn. kai prov tauta tiv ikanov;
2:17 ou gar esmen wv oi loipoi kaphleuontev ton logon tou
 yeou, all wv ex eilikrineiav, all wv ek yeou katenwpion
 tou yeou en cristw laloumen.

3:1 arcomeya palin eautouv sunistanein; ei mh crhzomen
 wv tinev sustatikwn epistolwn prov umav h ex umwn sustatikwn;
3:2 h epistolh hmwn umeiv este, eggegrammenh en taiv kardiaiv
 hmwn, ginwskomenh kai anaginwskomenh upo pantwn anyrwpwn,
3:3 faneroumenoi oti este epistolh cristou diakonhyeisa
 uf hmwn, eggegrammenh ou melani, alla pneumati yeou zwntov,
 ouk en plaxin liyinaiv, alla en plaxin kardiaiv sarkinaiv.

3:4 pepoiyhsin de toiauthn ecomen dia tou cristou prov ton
 yeon.
3:5 ouc oti ikanoi esmen af eautwn logisasyai ti wv ex eautwn,
 all h ikanothv hmwn ek tou yeou,
3:6 ov kai ikanwsen hmav diakonouv kainhv diayhkhv, ou grammatov,
 alla pneumatov: to gar gramma apoktennei, to de pneuma
 zwopoiei.
3:7 ei de h diakonia tou yanatou en grammasin entetupwmenh
 en liyoiv egenhyh en doxh, wste mh dunasyai atenisai touv
 uiouv israhl eiv to proswpon mwusewv dia thn doxan tou
 proswpou autou thn katargoumenhn,
3:8 pwv ouci mallon h diakonia tou pneumatov estai en doxh;
3:9 ei gar h diakonia thv katakrisewv doxa, pollw mallon
 perisseuei h diakonia thv dikaiosunhv en doxh.
3:10 kai gar oude dedoxastai to dedoxasmenon en toutw tw
 merei eneken thv uperballoushv doxhv.
3:11 ei gar to katargoumenon dia doxhv, pollw mallon to
 menon en doxh.
3:12 econtev oun toiauthn elpida pollh parrhsia crwmeya,
3:13 kai ou kayaper mwushv etiyei kalumma epi to proswpon
 eautou prov to mh atenisai touv uiouv israhl eiv to telov
 tou katargoumenou.
3:14 all epwrwyh ta nohmata autwn. acri gar thv shmeron
 to auto kalumma epi th anagnwsei thv palaiav diayhkhv menei,
 mh anakaluptomenon oti en cristw katargeitai,
3:15 all ewv shmeron, hnika anaginwsketai mwushv, kalumma
 epi thn kardian autwn keitai:
3:16 hnika d an epistreqh prov kurion, periaireitai to kalumma.
3:17 o de kuriov to pneuma estin: ou de to pneuma kuriou,
 ekei eleuyeria.
3:18 hmeiv de pantev anakekalummenw proswpw thn doxan kuriou
 katoptrizomenoi thn authn eikona metamorfoumeya apo doxhv
 eiv doxan, kayaper apo kuriou pneumatov.

4:1 dia touto, econtev thn diakonian tauthn kaywv hlehyhmen,
 ouk ekkakoumen,
4:2 all apeipameya ta krupta thv aiscunhv, mh peripatountev
 en panourgia mhde dolountev ton logon tou yeou, alla th
 fanerwsei thv alhyeiav sunistwntev eautouv prov pasan suneidhsin
 anyrwpwn enwpion tou yeou.
4:3 ei de kai estin kekalummenon to euaggelion hmwn, en toiv
 apollumenoiv estin kekalummenon,
4:4 en oiv o yeov tou aiwnov toutou etuflwsen ta nohmata
 twn apistwn eiv to mh augasai autoiv ton fwtismon tou euaggeliou
 thv doxhv tou cristou, ov estin eikwn tou yeou.
4:5 ou gar eautouv khrussomen, alla criston ihsoun kurion,
 eautouv de doulouv umwn dia ihsoun.
4:6 oti o yeov o eipwn ek skotouv fwv lamqai, ov elamqen
 en taiv kardiaiv hmwn prov fwtismon thv gnwsewv thv doxhv
 tou yeou en proswpw ihsou cristou.

4:7 ecomen de ton yhsauron touton en ostrakinoiv skeuesin,
 ina h uperbolh thv dunamewv h tou yeou kai mh ex hmwn,
4:8 en panti ylibomenoi all ou stenocwroumenoi, aporoumenoi
 all ouk exaporoumenoi,
4:9 diwkomenoi all ouk egkataleipomenoi, kataballomenoi
 all ouk apollumenoi,
4:10 pantote thn nekrwsin tou kuriou ihsou en tw swmati
 periferontev, ina kai h zwh tou ihsou en tw swmati hmwn
 fanerwyh.
4:11 aei gar hmeiv oi zwntev eiv yanaton paradidomeya dia
 ihsoun, ina kai h zwh tou ihsou fanerwyh en th ynhth sarki
 hmwn.
4:12 wste o men yanatov en hmin energeitai, h de zwh en
 umin.
4:13 econtev de to auto pneuma thv pistewv kata to gegrammenon,
 episteusa, dio elalhsa, kai hmeiv pisteuomen, dio kai laloumen,
 
4:14 eidotev oti o egeirav ton kurion ihsoun kai hmav dia
 ihsou egerei kai parasthsei sun umin.
4:15 ta gar panta di umav, ina h cariv pleonasasa dia twn
 pleionwn thn eucaristian perisseush eiv thn doxan tou yeou.

4:16 dio ouk ekkakoumen, all ei kai o exw hmwn anyrwpov
 diafyeiretai, all o eswyen anakainoutai hmera kai hmera.
4:17 to gar parautika elafron thv yliqewv hmwn kay uperbolhn
 eiv uperbolhn aiwnion barov doxhv katergazetai hmin,
4:18 mh skopountwn hmwn ta blepomena, alla ta mh blepomena:
 ta gar blepomena proskaira, ta de mh blepomena aiwnia.

5:1 oidamen gar oti ean h epigeiov hmwn oikia tou skhnouv
 kataluyh, oikodomhn ek yeou ecomen, oikian aceiropoihton
 aiwnion en toiv ouranoiv.
5:2 kai gar en toutw stenazomen, to oikhthrion hmwn to ex
 ouranou ependusasyai epipoyountev,
5:3 ei ge kai endusamenoi ou gumnoi eureyhsomeya.
5:4 kai gar oi ontev en tw skhnei stenazomen, baroumenoi
 ef w ou yelomen ekdusasyai, all ependusasyai, ina katapoyh
 to ynhton upo thv zwhv.
5:5 o de katergasamenov hmav eiv auto touto yeov, o kai
 douv hmin ton arrabwna tou pneumatov.
5:6 yarrountev oun pantote kai eidotev oti endhmountev en
 tw swmati ekdhmoumen apo tou kuriou:
5:7 dia pistewv gar peripatoumen, ou dia eidouv: --
5:8 yarroumen de kai eudokoumen mallon ekdhmhsai ek tou
 swmatov kai endhmhsai prov ton kurion.
5:9 dio kai filotimoumeya, eite endhmountev eite ekdhmountev,
 euarestoi autw einai.
5:10 touv gar pantav hmav fanerwyhnai dei emprosyen tou
 bhmatov tou cristou, ina komishtai ekastov ta dia tou swmatov
 prov a epraxen, eite agayon eite kakon.

5:11 eidotev oun ton fobon tou kuriou anyrwpouv peiyomen,
 yew de pefanerwmeya, elpizw de kai en taiv suneidhsesin
 umwn pefanerwsyai.
5:12 ou gar palin eautouv sunistanomen umin, alla aformhn
 didontev umin kauchmatov uper hmwn, ina echte prov touv
 en proswpw kaucwmenouv kai ou kardia.
5:13 eite gar exesthmen, yew, eite swfronoumen, umin.

5:14 h gar agaph tou cristou sunecei hmav, krinantav touto,
 oti [ei] eiv uper pantwn apeyanen, ara oi pantev apeyanon:
5:15 kai uper pantwn apeyanen, ina oi zwntev mhketi eautoiv
 zwsin, alla tw uper autwn apoyanonti kai egeryenti.
5:16 wste hmeiv apo tou nun oudena oidamen kata sarka: ei
 de kai egnwkamen kata sarka criston, alla nun ouketi ginwskomen.
5:17 wste ei tiv en cristw, kainh ktisiv: ta arcaia parhlyen,
 idou gegonen kaina ta panta.
5:18 ta de panta ek tou yeou tou katallaxantov hmav eautw
 dia ihsou cristou kai dontov hmin thn diakonian thv katallaghv,
5:19 wv oti yeov hn en cristw kosmon katallasswn eautw,
 mh logizomenov autoiv ta paraptwmata autwn, kai yemenov
 en hmin ton logon thv katallaghv.
5:20 uper cristou oun presbeuomen wv tou yeou parakalountov
 di hmwn: deomeya uper cristou, katallaghte tw yew:
5:21 ton gar mh gnonta amartian uper hmwn amartian epoihsen,
 ina hmeiv genwmeya dikaiosunh yeou en autw.

6:1 sunergountev de kai parakaloumen mh eiv kenon thn carin
 tou yeou dexasyai umav --
6:2 legei gar: kairw dektw ephkousa sou kai en hmera swthriav
 ebohyhsa soi: idou nun kairov euprosdektov, idou nun hmera
 swthriav --
6:3 mhdemian en mhdeni didontev proskophn, ina mh mwmhyh
 h diakonia,
6:4 all en panti sunistwntev eautouv wv yeou diakonoi, en
 upomonh pollh, en yliqesin, en anagkaiv, en stenocwriaiv,
6:5 en plhgaiv, en fulakaiv, en akatastasiaiv, en kopoiv,
 en agrupniaiv, en nhsteiaiv,
6:6 en agnothti, en gnwsei, en makroyumia, en crhstothti,
 en pneumati agiw, en agaph anupokritw,
6:7 en logw alhyeiav, en dunamei yeou, dia twn oplwn thv
 dikaiosunhv twn dexiwn kai aristerwn,
6:8 dia doxhv kai atimiav, dia dusfhmiav kai eufhmiav, wv
 planoi kai alhyeiv,
6:9 wv agnooumenoi kai epiginwskomenoi, wv apoynhskontev
 kai idou zwmen, wv paideuomenoi kai mh yanatoumenoi,
6:10 wv lupoumenoi aei de cairontev, wv ptwcoi pollouv de
 ploutizontev, wv mhden econtev kai panta katecontev.

6:11 to stoma hmwn anewgen prov umav, korinyioi, h kardia
 hmwn peplatuntai:
6:12 ou stenocwreisye en hmin, stenocwreisye de en toiv
 splagcnoiv umwn:
6:13 thn de authn antimisyian, wv teknoiv legw, platunyhte
 kai umeiv.

6:14 mh ginesye eterozugountev apistoiv: tiv gar metoch
 dikaiosunh kai anomia; tiv de koinwnia fwti prov skotov;
6:15 tiv de sumfwnhsiv cristw prov belial; h tiv meriv
 pistw meta apistou;
6:16 tiv de sugkatayesiv naw yeou meta eidwlwn; umeiv gar
 naov yeou este zwntov, kaywv eipen o yeov oti enoikhsw
 en autoiv kai emperipathsw, kai esomai autwn yeov, kai
 autoi esontai moi laov.
6:17 dio exelyate ek mesou autwn kai aforisyhte, legei kuriov,
 kai akayartou mh aptesye, kagw eisdexomai umav,
6:18 kai esomai umin eiv patera, kai umeiv esesye moi eiv
 uiouv kai yugaterav, legei kuriov pantokratwr.

7:1 tautav oun econtev tav epaggeliav, agaphtoi, kayariswmen
 eautouv apo pantov molusmou sarkov kai pneumatov, epitelountev
 agiwsunhn en fobw yeou.

7:2 cwrhsate hmav: oudena hdikhsamen, oudena efyeiramen,
 oudena epleonekthsamen.
7:3 ou prov katakrisin legw: proeirhka gar oti en taiv kardiaiv
 hmwn este eiv to sunapoyanein kai suzhn.
7:4 pollh moi parrhsia prov umav, pollh moi kauchsiv uper
 umwn: peplhrwmai th paraklhsei, uperperisseuomai th cara
 epi pash th yliqei hmwn.
7:5 kai gar elyontwn hmwn eiv makedonian oudemian eschken
 anesin h sarx hmwn, all en panti ylibomenoi: exwyen macai,
 eswyen foboi.
7:6 all o parakalwn touv tapeinouv parekalesen hmav o yeov
 en th parousia titou:
7:7 ou monon de en th parousia autou, alla kai en th paraklhsei
 h pareklhyh ef umin, anaggellwn hmin thn umwn epipoyhsin,
 ton umwn odurmon, ton umwn zhlon uper emou, wste me mallon
 carhnai,
7:8 oti ei kai eluphsa umav en th epistolh, ou metamelomai,
 ei kai metemelomhn: blepw gar oti h epistolh ekeinh, ei
 kai prov wran, eluphsen umav.
7:9 nun cairw, ouc oti eluphyhte, all oti eluphyhte eiv
 metanoian: eluphyhte gar kata yeon, ina en mhdeni zhmiwyhte
 ex hmwn.
7:10 h gar kata yeon luph metanoian eiv swthrian ametamelhton
 katergazetai: h de tou kosmou luph yanaton katergazetai.
7:11 idou gar auto touto, to kata yeon luphyhnai umav, poshn
 kateirgasato umin spoudhn, alla apologian, alla aganakthsin,
 alla fobon, alla epipoyhsin, alla zhlon, alla ekdikhsin!
 en panti sunesthsate eautouv agnouv einai en tw pragmati.
7:12 ara ei kai egraqa umin, ouc eineken tou adikhsantov,
 oude eineken tou adikhyentov, all eineken tou fanerwyhnai
 thn spoudhn umwn thn uper hmwn prov umav enwpion tou yeou.
7:13 dia touto parakeklhmeya. epi de th paraklhsei umwn perissoterwv
 mallon ecarhmen epi th cara titou, oti anapepautai to pneuma
 autou apo pantwn umwn:
7:14 oti ei ti autw uper umwn kekauchmai, ou kathscunyhn,
 all wv panta en alhyeia elalhsamen umin, outwv kai h kauchsiv
 hmwn h epi titou alhyeia egenhyh.
7:15 kai ta splagcna autou perissoterwv eiv umav estin anamimnhskomenou
 thn pantwn umwn upakohn, wv meta fobou kai tromou edexasye
 auton.
7:16 cairw oti en panti yarrw en umin.

8:1 gnwrizw de umin, adelfoi, thn carin tou yeou thn dedomenhn
 en taiv ekklhsiaiv thv makedoniav,
8:2 oti en pollh dokimh yliqewv h perisseia thv carav autwn
 kai h kata bayouv ptwceia autwn eperisseusen eiv ton plouton
 thv aplothtov autwn:
8:3 oti kata dunamin, marturw, kai uper dunamin, auyairetoi,
8:4 meta pollhv paraklhsewv deomenoi hmwn thn carin kai
 thn koinwnian thv diakoniav thv eiv touv agiouv,
8:5 kai ou kaywv hlpisamen, all eautouv edwkan prwton tw
 kuriw kai hmin dia yelhmatov yeou,
8:6 eiv to parakalesai hmav titon, ina kaywv proenhrxato
 outwv kai epitelesh eiv umav kai thn carin tauthn.
8:7 all wsper en panti perisseuete, pistei kai logw kai
 gnwsei kai pash spoudh kai th ex umwn en hmin agaph, ina
 kai en tauth th cariti perisseuhte.
8:8 ou kat epitaghn legw, alla dia thv eterwn spoudhv kai
 to thv umeterav agaphv gnhsion dokimazwn:
8:9 ginwskete gar thn carin tou kuriou hmwn ihsou cristou,
 oti di umav eptwceusen plousiov wn, ina umeiv th ekeinou
 ptwceia plouthshte.
8:10 kai gnwmhn en toutw didwmi: touto gar umin sumferei,
 oitinev ou monon to poihsai, alla kai to yelein proenhrxasye
 apo perusi:
8:11 nuni de kai to poihsai epitelesate, opwv kayaper h
 proyumia tou yelein, outwv kai to epitelesai ek tou ecein.
8:12 ei gar h proyumia prokeitai, kayo ean ech tiv euprosdektov,
 ou kayo ouk ecei.
8:13 ou gar ina alloiv anesiv, umin de yliqiv, all ex isothtov en tw
 nun kairw to umwn perisseuma eiv to ekeinwn usterhma,
8:14 ina kai to ekeinwn perisseuma genhtai eiv to umwn usterhma, opwv
 genhtai isothv,
8:15 kaywv gegraptai: o to polu ouk epleonasen, kai o to
 oligon ouk hlattonhsen.

8:16 cariv de tw yew tw didonti thn authn spoudhn uper umwn
 en th kardia titou,
8:17 oti thn men paraklhsin edexato, spoudaioterov de uparcwn
 auyairetov exhlyen prov umav.
8:18 sunepemqamen de met autou ton adelfon ou o epainov
 en tw euaggeliw dia paswn twn ekklhsiwn: --
8:19 ou monon de, alla kai ceirotonhyeiv upo twn ekklhsiwn
 sunekdhmov hmwn sun th cariti tauth th diakonoumenh uf
 hmwn prov thn autou tou kuriou doxan kai proyumian hmwn: --
8:20 stellomenoi touto, mh tiv hmav mwmhshtai en th adrothti
 tauth th diakonoumenh uf hmwn,
8:21 pronooumenoi kala ou monon enwpion kuriou, alla kai
 enwpion anyrwpwn.
8:22 sunepemqamen de autoiv ton adelfon hmwn, on edokimasamen
 en polloiv pollakiv spoudaion onta, nuni de polu spoudaioteron
 pepoiyhsei pollh th eiv umav.
8:23 eite uper titou, koinwnov emov kai eiv umav sunergov:
 eite adelfoi hmwn, apostoloi ekklhsiwn, doxa cristou.
8:24 thn oun endeixin thv agaphv umwn kai hmwn kauchsewv
 uper umwn eiv autouv endeixasye eiv proswpon twn ekklhsiwn.

9:1 peri men gar thv diakoniav thv eiv touv agiouv perisson
 moi estin to grafein umin:
9:2 oida gar thn proyumian umwn hn uper umwn kaucwmai makedosin,
 oti acaia pareskeuastai apo perusi: kai o ex umwn zhlov
 hreyisen touv pleionav.
9:3 epemqa de touv adelfouv, ina mh to kauchma hmwn to uper
 umwn kenwyh en tw merei toutw, ina, kaywv elegon, pareskeuasmenoi
 hte,
9:4 mhpwv ean elywsin sun emoi makedonev kai eurwsin umav
 aparaskeuastouv, kataiscunywmen hmeiv, ina mh legwmen umeiv,
 en th upostasei tauth thv kauchsewv.
9:5 anagkaion oun hghsamhn parakalesai touv adelfouv ina
 proelywsin eiv umav kai prokatartiswsin thn prokathggelmenhn
 eulogian umwn, tauthn etoimhn einai, outwv wv eulogian
 kai mh wv pleonexian.
9:6 touto de, o speirwn feidomenwv feidomenwv kai yerisei,
 kai o speirwn ep eulogiaiv ep eulogiaiv kai yerisei.
9:7 ekastov kaywv proaireitai th kardia, mh ek luphv h ex
 anagkhv: ilaron gar dothn agapa o yeov.
9:8 dunatov de o yeov pasan carin perisseusai eiv umav,
 ina en panti pantote pasan autarkeian econtev perisseuhte
 eiv pan ergon agayon,
9:9 kaywv gegraptai: eskorpisen, edwken toiv penhsin: h dikaiosunh
 autou menei eiv ton aiwna.
9:10 o de epicorhgwn sperma tw speironti kai arton eiv brwsin
 corhghsai kai plhyunai ton sporon umwn kai auxhsai ta genhmata
 thv dikaiosunhv umwn:
9:11 en panti ploutizomenoi eiv pasan aplothta, htiv katergazetai
 di hmwn eucaristian tw yew:
9:12 oti h diakonia thv leitourgiav tauthv ou monon estin
 prosanaplhrousa ta usterhmata twn agiwn, alla kai perisseuousa
 dia pollwn eucaristiwn tw yew: --
9:13 dia thv dokimhv thv diakoniav tauthv doxazontev ton
 yeon epi th upotagh thv omologiav umwn eiv to euaggelion
 tou cristou kai aplothti thv koinwniav eiv autouv kai eiv
 pantav,
9:14 kai autwn dehsei uper umwn, epipoyountwn umav dia thn
 uperballousan carin tou yeou ef umin.
9:15 cariv de tw yew epi th anekdihghtw autou dwrea.

10:1 autov de egw paulov parakalw umav dia thv praothtov
 kai epieikeiav tou cristou, ov kata proswpon men tapeinov
 en umin, apwn de yarrw eiv umav:
10:2 deomai de to mh parwn yarrhsai th pepoiyhsei h logizomai
 tolmhsai epi tinav touv logizomenouv hmav wv kata sarka
 peripatountav.
10:3 en sarki gar peripatountev ou kata sarka strateuomeya:
10:4 ta gar opla thv strateiav hmwn ou sarkika, alla dunata
 tw yew prov kayairesin ocurwmatwn: --
10:5 logismouv kayairountev kai pan uqwma epairomenon kata thv gnwsewv
 tou yeou, kai aicmalwtizontev pan nohma eiv thn upakohn tou cristou,
10:6 kai en etoimw econtev ekdikhsai pasan parakohn, otan
 plhrwyh umwn h upakoh.

10:7 ta kata proswpon blepete! ei tiv pepoiyen eautw cristou
 einai, touto logizesyw palin af eautou, oti kaywv autov
 cristou, outwv kai hmeiv cristou.
10:8 ean te gar [kai] perissoteron ti kauchswmai peri thv exousiav
 hmwn, hv edwken o kuriov hmin eiv oikodomhn kai ouk eiv
 kayairesin umwn, ouk aiscunyhsomai,
10:9 ina mh doxw wv an ekfobein umav dia twn epistolwn.
10:10 oti ai men epistolai, fhsin, bareiai kai iscurai, h
 de parousia tou swmatov asyenhv kai o logov exouyenhmenov.
10:11 touto logizesyw o toioutov, oti oioi esmen tw logw
 di epistolwn apontev, toioutoi kai parontev tw ergw.

10:12 ou gar tolmwmen egkrinai h sugkrinai eautouv tisin
 twn eautouv sunistanontwn: alla autoi en eautoiv eautouv
 metrountev kai sugkrinontev eautouv eautoiv ou suniousin.
10:13 hmeiv de ouci eiv ta ametra kauchsomeya, alla kata
 to metron tou kanonov ou emerisen hmin o yeov metrou, efikesyai
 acri kai umwn.
10:14 ou gar wv mh efiknoumenoi eiv umav uperekteinomen
 eautouv: acri gar kai umwn efyasamen en tw euaggeliw tou
 cristou,
10:15 ouk eiv ta ametra kaucwmenoi en allotrioiv kopoiv,
 elpida de econtev, auxanomenhv thv pistewv umwn, en umin
 megalunyhnai kata ton kanona hmwn eiv perisseian,
10:16 eiv ta uperekeina umwn euaggelisasyai, ouk en allotriw
 kanoni eiv ta etoima kauchsasyai.
10:17 o de kaucwmenov en kuriw kaucasyw:
10:18 ou gar o eauton sunistwn, ekeinov estin dokimov, all
 on o kuriov sunisthsin.

11:1 ofelon aneicesye mou mikron th afrosunh: alla kai anecesye
 mou.
11:2 zhlw gar umav yeou zhlw: hrmosamhn gar umav eni andri,
 paryenon agnhn parasthsai tw cristw:
11:3 foboumai de mhpwv, wv o ofiv euan exhpathsen en th
 panourgia autou, outwv fyarh ta nohmata umwn apo thv aplothtov
 thv eiv ton criston.
11:4 ei men gar o ercomenov allon ihsoun khrussei on ouk
 ekhruxamen, h pneuma eteron lambanete o ouk elabete, h
 euaggelion eteron o ouk edexasye, kalwv aneicesye.
11:5 logizomai gar mhden usterhkenai twn uperlian apostolwn.
11:6 ei de kai idiwthv tw logw, all ou th gnwsei, all en
 panti fanerwyentev en pasin eiv umav.
11:7 h amartian epoihsa emauton tapeinwn ina umeiv uqwyhte,
 oti dwrean to tou yeou euaggelion euhggelisamhn umin;
11:8 allav ekklhsiav esulhsa labwn oqwnion prov thn umwn
 diakonian,
11:9 kai parwn prov umav kai usterhyeiv ou katenarkhsa oudenov:
 to gar usterhma mou prosaneplhrwsan oi adelfoi elyontev
 apo makedoniav: kai en panti abarh umin emauton ethrhsa
 kai thrhsw.
11:10 estin alhyeia cristou en emoi oti h kauchsiv auth
 ou fraghsetai eiv eme en toiv klimasin thv acaiav.
11:11 diati; oti ouk agapw umav; o yeov oiden:
11:12 o de poiw, kai poihsw, ina ekkoqw thn aformhn twn
 yelontwn aformhn, ina en w kaucwntai eureywsin kaywv kai
 hmeiv.
11:13 oi gar toioutoi qeudapostoloi, ergatai dolioi, metaschmatizomenoi
 eiv apostolouv cristou.
11:14 kai ou yaumaston: autov gar o satanav metaschmatizetai
 eiv aggelon fwtov.
11:15 ou mega oun ei kai oi diakonoi autou metaschmatizontai
 wv diakonoi dikaiosunhv, wn to telov estai kata ta erga
 autwn.

11:16 palin legw, mh tiv me doxh afrona einai: ei de mh
 ge, kan wv afrona dexasye me, ina kagw mikron ti kauchswmai.
11:17 o lalw, ou lalw kata kurion, all wv en afrosunh, en
 tauth th upostasei thv kauchsewv.
11:18 epei polloi kaucwntai kata thn sarka, kagw kauchsomai.
11:19 hdewv gar anecesye twn afronwn fronimoi ontev:
11:20 anecesye gar ei tiv umav katadouloi, ei tiv katesyiei,
 ei tiv lambanei, ei tiv epairetai, ei tiv umav eiv proswpon
 derei.
11:21 kata atimian legw, wv oti hmeiv hsyenhsamen. en w
 d an tiv tolma, en afrosunh legw, tolmw kagw.
11:22 ebraioi eisin; kagw: israhlitai eisin; kagw: sperma
 abraam eisin; kagw:
11:23 diakonoi cristou eisin; parafronwn lalw, uper egw:
 en kopoiv perissoterwv, en plhgaiv uperballontwv, en fulakaiv
 perissoterwv, en yanatoiv pollakiv:
11:24 upo ioudaiwn pentakiv tessarakonta para mian elabon,
11:25 triv errabdisyhn, apax eliyasyhn, triv enauaghsa,
 nucyhmeron en tw buyw pepoihka:
11:26 odoiporiaiv pollakiv, kindunoiv potamwn, kindunoiv
 lhstwn, kindunoiv ek genouv, kindunoiv ex eynwn, kindunoiv
 en polei, kindunoiv en erhmia, kindunoiv en yalassh, kindunoiv
 en qeudadelfoiv:
11:27 en kopw kai mocyw, en agrupniaiv pollakiv, en limw
 kai diqei, en nhsteiaiv pollakiv, en qucei kai gumnothti:
11:28 cwriv twn parektov h episustasiv mou h kay hmeran,
 h merimna paswn twn ekklhsiwn.
11:29 tiv asyenei, kai ouk asyenw; tiv skandalizetai, kai
 ouk egw puroumai;
11:30 ei kaucasyai dei, ta thv asyeneiav mou kauchsomai.
11:31 o yeov kai pathr tou kuriou hmwn ihsou cristou oiden,
 o wn euloghtov eiv touv aiwnav, oti ou qeudomai.
11:32 en damaskw o eynarchv areta tou basilewv efrourei
 thn damaskhnwn polin piasai me yelwn,
11:33 kai dia yuridov en sarganh ecalasyhn dia tou teicouv
 kai exefugon tav ceirav autou.

12:1 kaucasyai dh ou sumferei moi: eleusomai gar eiv optasiav
 kai apokaluqeiv kuriou.
12:2 oida anyrwpon en cristw pro etwn dekatessarwn: eite
 en swmati ouk oida, eite ektov tou swmatov ouk oida, o
 yeov oiden: arpagenta ton toiouton ewv tritou ouranou.
12:3 kai oida ton toiouton anyrwpon: eite en swmati eite
 ektov tou swmatov ouk oida, o yeov oiden:
12:4 oti hrpagh eiv ton paradeison kai hkousen arrhta rhmata,
 a ouk exon anyrwpw lalhsai.
12:5 uper tou toioutou kauchsomai, uper de emautou ou kauchsomai
 ei mh en taiv asyeneiaiv mou.
12:6 ean gar yelhsw kauchsasyai, ouk esomai afrwn: alhyeian
 gar erw: feidomai de mh tiv eiv eme logishtai uper o blepei
 me h akouei ti ex emou.

12:7 kai th uperbolh twn apokaluqewn ina mh uperairwmai,
 edoyh moi skoloq th sarki, aggelov satan, ina me kolafizh
 ina mh uperairwmai.
12:8 uper toutou triv ton kurion parekalesa ina aposth ap
 emou:
12:9 kai eirhken moi: arkei soi h cariv mou: h gar dunamiv
 mou en asyeneia teleioutai. hdista oun mallon kauchsomai
 en taiv asyeneiaiv mou, ina episkhnwsh ep eme h dunamiv
 tou cristou.
12:10 dio eudokw en asyeneiaiv, en ubresin, en anagkaiv,
 en diwgmoiv, en stenocwriaiv, uper cristou: otan gar asyenw,
 tote dunatov eimi.

12:11 gegona afrwn kaucwmenov! umeiv me hnagkasate. egw
 gar wfeilon uf umwn sunistasyai: ouden gar usterhsa twn
 uperlian apostolwn, ei kai ouden eimi.
12:12 ta men shmeia tou apostolou kateirgasyh en umin en
 pash upomonh, en shmeioiv kai terasin kai dunamesin.
12:13 ti gar estin o htthyhte uper tav loipav ekklhsiav,
 ei mh oti autov egw ou katenarkhsa umwn; carisasye moi
 thn adikian tauthn.
12:14 idou triton etoimwv ecw elyein prov umav, kai ou katanarkhsw
 umwn: ou gar zhtw ta umwn, alla umav. ou gar ofeilei ta
 tekna toiv goneusin yhsaurizein, all oi goneiv toiv teknoiv.
12:15 egw de hdista dapanhsw kai ekdapanhyhsomai uper twn
 qucwn umwn, ei kai perissoterwv umav agapwn htton agapwmai.
12:16 estw de, egw ou katebarhsa umav, all uparcwn panourgov
 dolw umav elabon.
12:17 mh tina wn apestalka prov umav, di autou epleonekthsa
 umav;
12:18 parekalesa titon kai sunapesteila ton adelfon: mhti
 epleonekthsen umav titov; ou tw autw pneumati periepathsamen;
 ou toiv autoiv icnesin;

12:19 palin dokeite oti umin apologoumeya; katenwpion tou
 yeou en cristw laloumen: ta de panta, agaphtoi, uper thv
 umwn oikodomhv.
12:20 foboumai gar mhpwv elywn ouc oiouv yelw eurw umav,
 kagw eureyw umin oion ou yelete, mhpwv ereiv, zhloi, yumoi,
 eriyeiai, katalaliai, qiyurismoi, fusiwseiv, akatastasiai,
12:21 mh palin elyonta me tapeinwsh o yeov mou prov umav
 kai penyhsw pollouv twn prohmarthkotwn kai mh metanohsantwn
 epi th akayarsia kai porneia kai aselgeia h epraxan.

13:1 triton touto ercomai prov umav: epi stomatov duo marturwn
 kai triwn stayhsetai pan rhma.
13:2 proeirhka kai prolegw, wv parwn to deuteron, kai apwn
 nun grafw toiv prohmarthkosin kai toiv loipoiv pasin, oti
 ean elyw eiv to palin ou feisomai,
13:3 epei dokimhn zhteite tou en emoi lalountov cristou,
 ov eiv umav ouk asyenei, alla dunatei en umin.
13:4 kai gar ei estaurwyh ex asyeneiav, alla zh ek dunamewv
 yeou: kai gar hmeiv asyenoumen en autw, alla zhsomeya sun
 autw ek dunamewv yeou eiv umav.
13:5 eautouv peirazete ei este en th pistei, eautouv dokimazete.
 h ouk epiginwskete eautouv oti ihsouv cristov en umin estin;
 ei mh ti adokimoi este.
13:6 elpizw de oti gnwsesye oti hmeiv ouk esmen adokimoi.
13:7 eucomai de prov ton yeon mh poihsai umav kakon mhden,
 ouc ina hmeiv dokimoi fanwmen, all ina umeiv to kalon poihte,
 hmeiv de wv adokimoi wmen.
13:8 ou gar dunameya ti kata thv alhyeiav, all uper thv
 alhyeiav.
13:9 cairomen gar otan hmeiv asyenwmen, umeiv de dunatoi
 hte: touto de kai eucomeya, thn umwn katartisin.
13:10 dia touto tauta apwn grafw, ina parwn mh apotomwv
 crhswmai kata thn exousian hn edwken moi o kuriov eiv oikodomhn
 kai ouk eiv kayairesin.

13:11 loipon, adelfoi, cairete, katartizesye, parakaleisye,
 to auto froneite, eirhneuete, kai o yeov thv agaphv kai
 eirhnhv estai mey umwn.
13:12 aspasasye allhlouv en agiw filhmati. 

13:13 aspazontai umav oi agioi pantev.

13:14 h cariv tou kuriou ihsou cristou kai h agaph tou yeou
 kai h koinwnia tou agiou pneumatov meta pantwn umwn: amhn.
